+----------------------------------------------------+
+ Major K2 Agent Release 1.9.0 (Trinity) +
+----------------------------------------------------+
IC
========
- FTP client integration.
- Rollover logs upload support.
- Mount path and log path changes.
- Under privilege support. Implementation to get IP in case of host, container and k8s case.
- Application info update and creation of source identifier.
- IC control command integration, support for upload log, unsupported agent and logger level integration.
- Implementation to stop instrumentation and event sending in case of Unsupported agent.
- File inclusion and path traversal partial validation.
- Event Json update for identifier.
- Support for application port detection, added http server listen hook.
- Fix for file event generation for read and write streams.
- File watcher integration.
